      "properties": {
        "Node name for S&R": "Note"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "13 - ASSET FACTORY   concept -> HQ ortho views -> textured 3D asset\n\nSTEP 1 - CONCEPT (group 1, active):\n  Type your asset prompt, Run (~seconds). Iterate by editing the prompt or\n  bumping the Seed. Optional: enable the Reference nodes (Ctrl+B) to guide\n  with an image. KEEP the seed control on 'fixed' \u2014 that is what lets the\n  3D stages reuse the cached concept later.\n\nSTEP 2 - PRESS PLAY ON 3D (groups 2 + 2b + 3):\n  When you love the concept, select ALL nodes of groups 2, 2b and 3 and\n  press Ctrl+B to enable, then Run. The concept is NOT regenerated (cache).\n  Pipeline: 4 ortho views (~3.5 min) -> Flux2 detail pass at 1024 (~1 min)\n  -> Trellis 25-step Q8 mesh + 4096 texture bake (~8 min).\n  The Trellis FRONT view is your original concept image; MV-Adapter only\n  fills in back/left/right (enhanced before use).\n  Output: output/3D/13_ASSET_FACTORY_*.glb (200k faces, Xatlas UVs, 4096\n  texture) + ASSET_VIEWS_HQ_* (the enhanced view sheet).\n\nIn Blender: File > Import > glTF. Views = your modeling/paintover reference.\nQuality knobs: detail-pass denoise (0.25-0.35), Trellis steps, target faces,\ntexture_size. Speed fallback: GGUF Q4_K_M + 12 steps + 2048 texture."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#432"
    }
